snippet.title: Dangle (Nitrome.com) Levels 1-9
snippet.description:
Levels 1 to 9 of the game Dangle, from Nitrome.com.
In this game created in 2007 you play as a spider trying to get down to the floor by cimbing with its rope. 
You can play it for free in: http://www.nitrome.com/games/dangle/?game=dangle#.X8WGi85JxPY
I hope you like it!
